</ul>

<p>Below are a few purposes that I think important in my early 20s to focus and execute on:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Engaged work and consistent learning at Google.</li>
  <li>Bodybuilding, weight loss, and basketball.</li>
  <li>Build connections and influence others.</li>
</ul>

